ZH: 他在花园里摆荡着秋千。
EN: He swings on the swing in the garden.

ZH: 她坐在摇椅上摆荡，享受着阳光。
EN: She sits in the rocking chair, swinging back and forth, enjoying the sunlight.

ZH: 孩子们在游乐场上摆荡着，笑声不断。
EN: The children swing back and forth at the playground, laughter filling the air.

ZH: 在海边的吊床上摆荡，感觉如此舒服。
EN: Swinging on the hammock by the beach feels so comfortable.

ZH: 他用力摆荡着篮球，试图投进篮筐。
EN: He swings the basketball forcefully, trying to make a shot.

ZH: 猴子在树枝上摆荡，敏捷而灵活。
EN: The monkey swings on the branches, agile and nimble.

