EN: The fruit trees are filled with ripe fruits, swaying in the gentle breeze.

ZH: 老人默默地坐在摇椅上摆荡，享受宁静的时光。
EN: The old man sits quietly on the rocking chair, swinging back and forth, enjoying the peaceful moments.

